sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant D as Dispatcher
    participant P as Plan File
    participant W as Worker
    participant M as Monitor
    participant IPC as IPC Directory

    U->>D: /dispatch "task description"
    D->>D: Read ~/.dispatch/config.yaml<br/>Resolve model → backend → command

    D->>P: Create plan.md with checklist
    D->>IPC: mkdir ipc/

    D-->>W: Spawn background worker
    D-->>M: Spawn background monitor
    D->>U: "Dispatched task-id using model"

    loop For each checklist item
        W->>W: Do the work
        W->>P: Mark item [x]
    end

    alt Worker needs clarification
        W->>IPC: Write 001.question (atomic)
        M->>IPC: Detect unanswered question
        M->>D: Exit → triggers notification
        D->>IPC: Read 001.question
        D->>U: Surface question
        U->>D: Answer
        D->>IPC: Write 001.answer (atomic)
        D-->>M: Respawn monitor
        W->>IPC: Detect answer, write 001.done
        W->>W: Continue working
    end

    W->>IPC: Write .done (all items complete)
    M->>IPC: Detect .done
    M->>D: Exit → triggers notification
    D->>P: Read final plan.md
    D->>U: Report results
